Paper: hep-th/0205075

Date: 2002-05-08

Title: Rudiments of Holography

Authors: Enrique Alvarez, Jorge Conde and Lorenzo Hernandez

Comments: 60 pages, additional misprints corrected, references added

An elementary introduction to Maldacena's AdS/CFT correspondence is given,with some emphasis in the Fefferman-Graham construction. This is based onlectures given by one of us (E.A.) at the Universidad Autonoma de Madrid.